{"work":"KJV + Strong's","code":"3Jo","book":"3 John","chapterCount":1,"chapters":[{"number":1,"verses":[{"id":"3Jo|1|1","reference":"3 John 1:1","number":1,"text":"The elder unto the wellbeloved Gaius, whom I love in the truth.","strongs":[{"label":"The elder","strongsId":"G4245"},{"label":"unto the wellbeloved","strongsId":"G27"},{"label":"Gaius","strongsId":"G1050"},{"label":"whom","strongsId":"G3739"},{"label":"I","strongsId":"G1473"},{"label":"love","strongsId":"G25"},{"label":"in","strongsId":"G1722"},{"label":"the truth","strongsId":"G225"}]},{"id":"3Jo|1|2","reference":"3 John 1:2","number":2,"text":"Beloved, I wish above all things that thou mayest prosper and be in health, even as thy soul prospereth.","strongs":[{"label":"Beloved","strongsId":"G27"},{"label":"I wish","strongsId":"G2172"},{"label":"above","strongsId":"G4012"},{"label":"all things","strongsId":"G3956"},{"label":"that thou","strongsId":"G4571"},{"label":"mayest prosper","strongsId":"G2137"},{"label":"and","strongsId":"G2532"},{"label":"be in health","strongsId":"G5198"},{"label":"even as","strongsId":"G2531"},{"label":"thy","strongsId":"G4675"},{"label":"soul","strongsId":"G5590"},{"label":"prospereth","strongsId":"G2137"}]},{"id":"3Jo|1|3","reference":"3 John 1:3","number":3,"text":"For I rejoiced greatly, when the brethren came and testified of the truth that is in thee, even as thou walkest in the truth.","strongs":[{"label":"For","strongsId":"G1063"},{"label":"I rejoiced","strongsId":"G5463"},{"label":"greatly","strongsId":"G3029"},{"label":"when the brethren","strongsId":"G80"},{"label":"came","strongsId":"G2064"},{"label":"and","strongsId":"G2532"},{"label":"testified","strongsId":"G3140"},{"label":"of the truth","strongsId":"G225"},{"label":"that is in thee","strongsId":"G4675"},{"label":"even as","strongsId":"G2531"},{"label":"thou","strongsId":"G4771"},{"label":"walkest","strongsId":"G4043"},{"label":"in","strongsId":"G1722"},{"label":"the truth","strongsId":"G225"}]},{"id":"3Jo|1|4","reference":"3 John 1:4","number":4,"text":"I have no greater joy than to hear that my children walk in truth.","strongs":[{"label":"I have","strongsId":"G2192"},{"label":"no","strongsId":"G3756"},{"label":"greater","strongsId":"G3186"},{"label":"greater","strongsId":"G5130"},{"label":"joy","strongsId":"G5479"},{"label":"than to","strongsId":"G2443"},{"label":"hear","strongsId":"G191"},{"label":"that my","strongsId":"G1699"},{"label":"children","strongsId":"G5043"},{"label":"walk","strongsId":"G4043"},{"label":"in","strongsId":"G1722"},{"label":"truth","strongsId":"G225"}]},{"id":"3Jo|1|5","reference":"3 John 1:5","number":5,"text":"Beloved, thou doest faithfully whatsoever thou doest to the brethren, and to strangers;","strongs":[{"label":"Beloved","strongsId":"G27"},{"label":"thou doest","strongsId":"G4160"},{"label":"faithfully","strongsId":"G4103"},{"label":"whatsoever","strongsId":"G3739"},{"label":"whatsoever","strongsId":"G1437"},{"label":"thou doest","strongsId":"G2038"},{"label":"to","strongsId":"G1519"},{"label":"the brethren","strongsId":"G80"},{"label":"and","strongsId":"G2532"},{"label":"to","strongsId":"G1519"},{"label":"strangers","strongsId":"G3581"}]},{"id":"3Jo|1|6","reference":"3 John 1:6","number":6,"text":"Which have borne witness of thy charity before the church: whom if thou bring forward on their journey after ➔ a godly sort, thou shalt do well:","strongs":[{"label":"Which","strongsId":"G3739"},{"label":"have borne witness","strongsId":"G3140"},{"label":"of thy","strongsId":"G4675"},{"label":"charity","strongsId":"G26"},{"label":"before","strongsId":"G1799"},{"label":"the church","strongsId":"G1577"},{"label":"whom","strongsId":"G3739"},{"label":"if thou bring forward on their journey","strongsId":"G4311"},{"label":"after","strongsId":"G516"},{"label":"a godly","strongsId":"G2316"},{"label":"sort","strongsId":"G516"},{"label":"thou shalt do","strongsId":"G4160"},{"label":"well","strongsId":"G2573"}]},{"id":"3Jo|1|7","reference":"3 John 1:7","number":7,"text":"Because that for ➔ his name's sake they went forth, taking nothing of the Gentiles.","strongs":[{"label":"Because that","strongsId":"G1063"},{"label":"for","strongsId":"G5228"},{"label":"his","strongsId":"G846"},{"label":"name's","strongsId":"G3686"},{"label":"sake","strongsId":"G5228"},{"label":"they went forth","strongsId":"G1831"},{"label":"taking","strongsId":"G2983"},{"label":"nothing","strongsId":"G3367"},{"label":"of","strongsId":"G575"},{"label":"the Gentiles","strongsId":"G1484"}]},{"id":"3Jo|1|8","reference":"3 John 1:8","number":8,"text":"We therefore ought to receive such, that we might be fellowhelpers to the truth.","strongs":[{"label":"We","strongsId":"G2249"},{"label":"therefore","strongsId":"G3767"},{"label":"ought","strongsId":"G3784"},{"label":"to receive","strongsId":"G618"},{"label":"such","strongsId":"G5108"},{"label":"that","strongsId":"G2443"},{"label":"we might be","strongsId":"G1096"},{"label":"fellowhelpers","strongsId":"G4904"},{"label":"to the truth","strongsId":"G225"}]},{"id":"3Jo|1|9","reference":"3 John 1:9","number":9,"text":"I wrote unto the church: but Diotrephes, who loveth to have the preeminence among them, receiveth us not.","strongs":[{"label":"I wrote","strongsId":"G1125"},{"label":"unto the church","strongsId":"G1577"},{"label":"but","strongsId":"G235"},{"label":"Diotrephes","strongsId":"G1361"},{"label":"who","strongsId":"G3588"},{"label":"loveth to have the preeminence","strongsId":"G5383"},{"label":"among them","strongsId":"G846"},{"label":"receiveth","strongsId":"G1926"},{"label":"us","strongsId":"G2248"},{"label":"not","strongsId":"G3756"}]},{"id":"3Jo|1|10","reference":"3 John 1:10","number":10,"text":"Wherefore, if I come, I will remember his deeds which he doeth, prating against us with malicious words: and not content therewith, neither doth ➔ he himself receive the brethren, and forbiddeth them that would, and casteth them out of the church.","strongs":[{"label":"Wherefore","strongsId":"G1223"},{"label":"Wherefore","strongsId":"G5124"},{"label":"if","strongsId":"G1437"},{"label":"I come","strongsId":"G2064"},{"label":"I will remember","strongsId":"G5279"},{"label":"his","strongsId":"G846"},{"label":"deeds","strongsId":"G2041"},{"label":"which","strongsId":"G3739"},{"label":"he doeth","strongsId":"G4160"},{"label":"prating against","strongsId":"G5396"},{"label":"us","strongsId":"G2248"},{"label":"with","strongsId":"G3056"},{"label":"malicious words","strongsId":"G4190"},{"label":"and","strongsId":"G2532"},{"label":"not","strongsId":"G3361"},{"label":"content","strongsId":"G714"},{"label":"therewith","strongsId":"G1909"},{"label":"therewith","strongsId":"G5125"},{"label":"neither","strongsId":"G3777"},{"label":"doth","strongsId":"G1926"},{"label":"he himself","strongsId":"G846"},{"label":"receive","strongsId":"G1926"},{"label":"the brethren","strongsId":"G80"},{"label":"and","strongsId":"G2532"},{"label":"forbiddeth","strongsId":"G2967"},{"label":"them that would","strongsId":"G1014"},{"label":"and","strongsId":"G2532"},{"label":"casteth","strongsId":"G1544"},{"label":"them out of","strongsId":"G1537"},{"label":"the church","strongsId":"G1577"}]},{"id":"3Jo|1|11","reference":"3 John 1:11","number":11,"text":"Beloved, follow not that which is evil, but that which is good. He that doeth good is of God: but he that doeth evil hath ➔ not seen God.","strongs":[{"label":"Beloved","strongsId":"G27"},{"label":"follow","strongsId":"G3401"},{"label":"not","strongsId":"G3361"},{"label":"that which is evil","strongsId":"G2556"},{"label":"but","strongsId":"G235"},{"label":"that which is good","strongsId":"G18"},{"label":"He that doeth good","strongsId":"G15"},{"label":"is","strongsId":"G2076"},{"label":"of","strongsId":"G1537"},{"label":"God","strongsId":"G2316"},{"label":"but","strongsId":"G1161"},{"label":"he that doeth evil","strongsId":"G2554"},{"label":"hath","strongsId":"G3708"},{"label":"not","strongsId":"G3756"},{"label":"seen","strongsId":"G3708"},{"label":"God","strongsId":"G2316"}]},{"id":"3Jo|1|12","reference":"3 John 1:12","number":12,"text":"Demetrius hath good report of all men, and of the truth itself: yea, and we also bear record; and ye know that our record is true.","strongs":[{"label":"Demetrius","strongsId":"G1216"},{"label":"hath good report","strongsId":"G3140"},{"label":"of","strongsId":"G5259"},{"label":"all","strongsId":"G3956"},{"label":"men, and","strongsId":"G2532"},{"label":"of","strongsId":"G5259"},{"label":"the truth","strongsId":"G225"},{"label":"itself","strongsId":"G846"},{"label":"yea","strongsId":"G1161"},{"label":"and","strongsId":"G2532"},{"label":"we","strongsId":"G2249"},{"label":"also bear record","strongsId":"G3140"},{"label":"and","strongsId":"G2532"},{"label":"ye know","strongsId":"G1492"},{"label":"that","strongsId":"G3754"},{"label":"our","strongsId":"G2257"},{"label":"record","strongsId":"G3141"},{"label":"is","strongsId":"G2076"},{"label":"true","strongsId":"G227"}]},{"id":"3Jo|1|13","reference":"3 John 1:13","number":13,"text":"I had many things to write, but I will not with ink and pen write unto thee:","strongs":[{"label":"I had","strongsId":"G2192"},{"label":"many things","strongsId":"G4183"},{"label":"to write","strongsId":"G1125"},{"label":"but","strongsId":"G235"},{"label":"I will","strongsId":"G2309"},{"label":"not","strongsId":"G3756"},{"label":"with","strongsId":"G1223"},{"label":"ink","strongsId":"G3188"},{"label":"and","strongsId":"G2532"},{"label":"pen","strongsId":"G2563"},{"label":"write","strongsId":"G1125"},{"label":"unto thee","strongsId":"G4671"}]},{"id":"3Jo|1|14","reference":"3 John 1:14","number":14,"text":"But I trust I shall ➔ shortly see thee, and we shall speak face to face. Peace be to thee. Our friends salute thee. Greet the friends by name.","strongs":[{"label":"But","strongsId":"G1161"},{"label":"I trust","strongsId":"G1679"},{"label":"I shall","strongsId":"G1492"},{"label":"shortly","strongsId":"G2112"},{"label":"see","strongsId":"G1492"},{"label":"thee","strongsId":"G4571"},{"label":"and","strongsId":"G2532"},{"label":"we shall speak","strongsId":"G2980"},{"label":"face","strongsId":"G4750"},{"label":"to","strongsId":"G4314"},{"label":"face","strongsId":"G4750"},{"label":"Peace","strongsId":"G1515"},{"label":"be to thee","strongsId":"G4671"},{"label":"Our friends","strongsId":"G5384"},{"label":"salute","strongsId":"G782"},{"label":"thee","strongsId":"G4571"},{"label":"Greet","strongsId":"G782"},{"label":"the friends","strongsId":"G5384"},{"label":"by","strongsId":"G2596"},{"label":"name","strongsId":"G3686"}]}]}]}
